{"tid":1739992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朱媛手足請你入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-11-19T20:58:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T11:04:14.000Z","uid":55552,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0bfded7f7315b1daf7ff4b91b8b6dd59075e8291","tid":1739992,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T20:58:29.000Z","msg":"我只係想同你講聲多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢幾日辛苦晒你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你同所有勇武手足永遠都係我嘅偶像。<br />\n<br />\n我知道呢幾日唔同地方都有關於你嘅討論，你睇完可能會覺得唔好受，但我希望你明白，其實我哋唔係針對你個人，只係不滿你背後嘅人嘅特權階級，同埋有啲手足為咗救人諗咗好多屎橋，但我哋無惡意，只係救人心切，絕對唔係想利用你當你condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好因為走咗覺得自責，子彈係唔會因為你姓氏轉彎，更加莫講話班黑警差啲想出實彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你嘅付出同犠牲唔少得過其他手足，而且我相信你已經盡力做咗你可以做嘅事，所以真係唔需要自責。<br />\n<br />\n最後我想講，一個人係無辦法選擇係邊個家庭出世，你企得出嚟，無論你係狗仔狗女定邊個邊個個孫，你都係我哋手足，我愛你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"603593b8de1ef64a48c8698d9493a75431d51027","tid":1739992,"uid":279326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T21:09:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">連豬一早有預兆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"6a4612bc7ea61016c38749112c5464a1e878f1f1","tid":1739992,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T21:40:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7c33de7691579c3b3e59f7c99afac8c5391ecc6","tid":1739992,"uid":293951,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T21:44:34.000Z","msg":"我都係咁話<br />\n知道自己有d背景而有良知的情況下選擇留低<br />\nRESPECT！感恩！"},{"pid":"0d35afb8effcc9c2131aea8480b23d208c3ecf41","tid":1739992,"uid":333488,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T21:52:03.000Z","msg":"「朱媛」真身年逾30　消息：已涉暴動被捕<br />\n過去數日理大一役，在多名學生獲准撤離下，局勢稍歇。不過，前立法會主席曾鈺成、與港大法律系講師張達明，在理大現場尋找「朱媛」一事，卻意外掀起一場小插曲。「朱媛」的身份引發諸多揣測，有關她是前國務院總理朱鎔基孫女的傳聞更甚器塵上，曾鈺成予以否認。消息指，朱鎔基並無孫女，而是次的「朱媛」在香港出生，年逾30，事後亦涉「參與暴動」被捕，相關傳聞不攻而破<br />\n<br />\n炒左車！唔好再搞真手足喇！"},{"pid":"ec5802bc7ea7c8fa8cb2e06415d3d040547fb308","tid":1739992,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T23:16:30.000Z","msg":"有錫建制報道聲稱，朱熔基有一仔一女，個仔朱雲來並無仔，是以「孫女」一事並非事實。朱熔基嘅女朱燕來曾喺中銀香港做嘢，佢有個女仔，所以朱熔基有一個外孫女，但外孫女唔姓朱，已經讀完書做三年，據稱其外孫女而家男朋友都未有，而且佢目前喺北京。"},{"pid":"1176d5f26e9952b0df77f4147bc6d48cf5c62855","tid":1739992,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T05:44:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e20a2b9cf4b53b72bdb4859f340e75feba7fba9","tid":1739992,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:30:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ef0246e30ae632cae727ac1853ccde357d8f1c","tid":1739992,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:55:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c336e6de7030a931a5fded2f2c97cf6e5dd6ac9","tid":1739992,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:38:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/udlbe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fudlbe&d=UXFjm%2BDMXm%2Fj1yL9MgXeqKcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=7879418e\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/udlbe</a>"},{"pid":"a0082db65